data.title: Fun, local, original
data.text: I pop into Stash about once a month to pick up Bison Brew, a locally roasted coffee, and always end up with more than I came for.  Lots of unusual greeting cards & gift wrap.  Cute clothes, belts & hats that can't be found other places.  Jewelry & purses are cute too.

data.title: Hip little gift shop in downtown Norman.
data.text: This gift shop has a cool mix of old and new and fair trade gifts. It's got an easy local feel to it. Some of the things we looked at were turquoise jewelry, candles, vintage furniture, handmade bags, art, and greeting cards. Worth the trip just to look around especially if you're going to be in downtown Norman. Wish there were more shops like this one.
